name: Going Home (Jellybean, funza)
description:
Going Home

This game was created as part of Global Game Jam 2023 in Cardiff at The Vault Arcade.

Pryderi defeated his opponent Math fab Mathonwy, with her best armour and a weapon that she obtained on her journey, after the last battle our hero returns home from the fortress of Cear Sidi, on the way home she encounters stragglers that she did not kill on the first pass through when she set out to kill Math fab Mathonwy. Precisely, they run away. Unfortunately, her equipment after so many battles start to break, and she starts to struggle with even regular monsters. She is worried that she will not make it home, but she will fight until her last breath. She thought that the worst is behind her, but it was only the start. 

This game was made by 6 people.

Bern Mold - 2D Art

Ciaran Jai Cosway - Audio, Music

James Miles - Programming

Jan Nechvatal - Game Design, Level Design

Josh Griffiths - Programming

William Grant - Audio, Music
